  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:10px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4185185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b561593&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltrL4iap3IaBeotUAvLJLEwiaRgUnKLa4ECYX2GemWEr5sx1b3zlzKg77A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">嗨大家好！我是阿真！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">前段时间就有朋友每天催我说海螺2.3视频模型在内测了，可惜我没有内测机会，只能等上线了再测试。还好 Lovart 接入模型超快，加上最近爆火的 LTX-2 模型它也接了，趁着 Hailuo 2.3 和 LTX 2 年费会员有一个月限免，我火速测试了一番来给大家汇报一下。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">上链接👉 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 79, 235);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.lovart.ai/zh/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lovart.ai/zh/</a></span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);line-height:1.6;border-style:dashed;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">目录</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-bottom: 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-size:medium;flex-flow:row;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;background-color:rgba(200, 196, 248, 0.24);border-radius:8px;word-spacing:0px;place-items:flex-start;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-width:1px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:16px 16px 10px;margin:10px 0px;display:flex;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgb(200, 196, 248);text-transform:none;max-width:100%;justify-content:flex-start;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 92.618%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 4px;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all;font-size:100%;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-family:PingFangSC-light;box-sizing:border-box;\"></p>\n       <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n        <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图像分层</span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lovart x Hailuo 2.3</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lovart x LTX 2</span></span></p>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小结</span></p>\n        </li>\n       </ol>\n       <p></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);line-height:1.6;border-style:dashed;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图像分层</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频模型测评开始前，插播一条设计方面的更新。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">不务正业 · 阿真终于想起了自己的设计老本行，分享一个Lovart 利好设计的新功能，图像分层。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图像分层的好处很多，可以方便独立编辑和控制，分层以后，我们可以对于不同的元素去进行修改，尤其方便小面积的修改。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单演示下。做海报的话，模型我优先选择Seedream 4。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">给到主体图片参考，让Lovart 生成海报。得到示例海报后，选择图片，点击【编辑元素】可拆分，拆完以后会得到文字、主体、背景，成为可编辑素材。后续不用再去重做整个图，可以单独改某一层不影响其他图层，复用其他图层或元素也会很方便👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=02552f22&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltSfZ2TRmVpsNz6nlO0SfqAuic7hvicQjakibIXFp3QKophqNWLy0w8dDRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里目前存在一个问题，拆完以后可能标题字直接成了纯文字了，想要保留字体效果，有个简单的办法就是，放大该图片，截图截取标题部分，然后选择【移除背景】抠图👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.36944444444444446\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=91c09631&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltmNqENibEsFFE6xIcaZmuzbnGQ18aT4EGiapd5XlCZvk6ia7MzvMzA9Jrw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">想修改文字但沿用字体效果，可以选择图片发送到对话，然后要求它修改文字内容。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果替换主体，发现将抠好图的主体放上去后光影完全不融合，我这里有一个好用的提示词用于融合调整光影，选中底图和主体图然后输入下方提示词👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-bottom: 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-size:medium;flex-flow:row;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;background-color:rgba(215, 212, 212, 0.14);border-radius:8px;word-spacing:0px;place-items:flex-start;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-width:1px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:16px 16px 10px;margin:10px 0px;display:flex;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgba(215, 212, 212, 0.14);text-transform:none;max-width:100%;justify-content:flex-start;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 0 1 auto;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"margin:0px 0px 4px;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all;font-size:87.5%;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-family:PingFangSC-light;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">保持主体与背景不变，自动校正环境光与主光源方向，使舞台灯光与角色反射光一致。调整色温与亮度平衡，让角色的阴影、反光、边缘光与舞台光效自然衔接。增加柔和漫射光和体积光，让整体氛围光统一、层次更立体，避免主体显得独立或突兀。优化整体光影协调度与真实感。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面是Lovart基于原图，拆分后增加了新的元素，基于图片和提示词，校正了光源，添加了阴影，也有修改角度的尝试（潮玩元素是后面放上去的，后一张3图对比中，图一是原图，图二图三是它调整了光影效果后的输出图）👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49444444444444446\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e0ed27b0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDlt0JJSts78AefDVZBtMQOE6WkImSyrZzFrWLAkAxbZvvdyMzqicuHL8Qw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6148148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2fb262a3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltCkLRKqwNj8ZrpIVRNnVbru6qrn8icACbxXoRqYI32QQh0L9yNyPwFiag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">拆装其他类型的海报和元素也都很简单，这样就不用再打开其他修图软件拼图了。并且文字拆分后都可以编辑，有提取文字需求也方便。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原图与拆分👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6166666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa754a0e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltcpsLjFZj3GvsAugx4p2jbgjkS6cuZ2v3sbhyMjaAmrGRvHm4W4hxyA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);line-height:1.6;border-style:dashed;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lovart x Hailuo 2.3</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hailuo 的模型原本在动漫和艺术风格上就很有优势，输出也稳定，加上 Hailuo 2.3 的舞蹈打斗大动态和微表情等据说都有再次提升，这次我先尝试了一个纯水墨打斗，《少年打虎》👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里稍微展开一点分享一下制作过程，制作一个极简的小短片，我觉得大致可以概括为5步。这里仅代表我个人习惯，仅供参考：</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-bottom: 20px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-size:medium;flex-flow:row;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;background-color:rgba(215, 212, 212, 0.14);border-radius:8px;word-spacing:0px;place-items:flex-start;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-width:1px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:16px 16px 10px;margin:10px 0px;display:flex;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgba(215, 212, 212, 0.14);text-transform:none;max-width:100%;justify-content:flex-start;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 0 1 auto;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"margin:0px 0px 4px;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all;font-size:87.5%;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-family:PingFangSC-light;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1. 想法到剧本</span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2. 剧本到生图提示词</span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 3. 提示词生成AI图像</span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 4. AI图像生成视频</span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 5. 后期剪辑与配音配乐</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">前四步我基本是在 Lovart&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-size-adjust: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">完成的，使用的模型如下👇</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7194444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8664462f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltviczvcNZIruMSV3CjQDWqzEP94ASicFDe0JRAw1GA1JPb8Xlz0dzDIpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">来了都是自己人，感兴趣可以看看我整个生图流程的回放，不过生成视频是从左边发起生成的，记录里就没有了👉&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 79, 235);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.lovart.ai/r/vwa0nb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lovart.ai/r/vwa0nb5</a></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">最开始我只有一个模糊的想法，就是少年和老虎搏斗，水墨质感的视频。于是我让 V7 模型生成了一系列少年和老虎的场景供我参考。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我选中了其中一张我比较喜欢的图片，然后选择Seedream 4 延展出正面全身照方便后面延展分镜图的时候作为参考👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 33%;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 97%;height: auto;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(200, 196, 248) 1px 1px 2px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d4990536&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltgCSrI5RNFm18ev4IicDEZrLq8iabL6LmXblZ5bv4m2O9iauXxlJTR6ByA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 33%;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 97%;height: auto;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(200, 196, 248) 1px 1px 2px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5023474178403755\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"852\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=893585b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltG1tfFfu8kf53ib5SBMOsodm7ARudiaYngyibTWUHyR8XP6acjfyPiaW6ibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 33%;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 97%;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(200, 196, 248) 1px 1px 2px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5023474178403755\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"852\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97ab5845&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltZq8aMdX94Y6S877YQJ12MnWFsrfzTMBaL6PyD8awFUDw0FXdHULKHA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后让 Seedream 4 生成了分镜图后，我意识到可能有色彩的不如纯水墨的效果统一，于是我修改了要求，生成了统一的纯水墨质感的黑白图片作为首帧图。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个小分享，生成分镜这里我有一套简易提示词和后续补充供参考👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"markdown\"><code><span leaf=\"\">生成8个独立但连贯的分镜描述，主题“少年打虎”，色调为黑白，风格为写实冒险。少年：14岁少年，衣衫褴褛、手持木棍，表情从恐惧到坚毅。老虎：成年孟加拉虎，凶猛咆哮。场景从山林遭遇到河流边决战。 &nbsp;</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">每个分镜格式： &nbsp;</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__bullet\">-</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__strong\">**分镜X**</span>： [镜头角度，例如：中景从少年视角] &nbsp;</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__bullet\">-</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__strong\">**描述**</span>： [详细视觉元素：动作、表情、颜色、光影、背景细节，50-80字]。 &nbsp;</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">输出为编号列表，确保动态感强、节奏递进。避免暴力血腥，强调英雄主义。</span></code><br><code></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">要有对峙镜头、特写表情、不同构图的分镜图。</span></code><br><code></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">继续增加分镜图，老虎把少年压倒在地，低角度视角，压迫感；少年跳起来俯视老虎，过肩俯视视角；老虎趴倒全景；少年跳到老虎背上，揪住老虎的毛发，俯视角度，等等，注意背后场景保持不变。</span></code><br></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成了图片后，我使用了 Hailuo 2.3 生成视频，在动态、表情、打斗场景上 Hailuo 2.3 效果都挺好所以我都用Hailuo 2.3（主要是这个月我有无限免费🤣）视频模型。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">有一个例外，就是有一个场景我想让少年说话，让他叫醒老虎。这个地方我改用了Wan 2.5 视频模型，因为它可以音画同步并且中文语音字正腔圆，另外大家在视频里听见少年说话也是对口型了的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">召唤视频生成和修改视频模型的方法如下👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6592592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=65568e73&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltFibmEXm69C2jc1B87ICXib5qly4g3YXzlw4G79lf1BnDdoRvgriakH0rw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我是8月底开的年会员，上面这个视频生图Midjourney V7和Seedream 4免费无限，Hailuo 2.3限时免费无限，从头到尾一共就花了130积分。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">爽玩。再来一个。《生活在海里的女孩》👇</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面这个流程和前面差不多，更简单。我之前随机抽卡抽了一张图，是这样的，觉得好看但是也没想好有什么用👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5601851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1382b670&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDlticxZwuOias7KL9wDaWaLaTfSiarW02dv6fmc2bXOx1G7OkFx3B97Axibdw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后昨天翻自己过往的图的时候灵光一现，想做一个生活在海里的女孩的小短片。没有什么故事剧情，就是单纯想让它生成女孩生活在海里，整个氛围比较静谧和治愈，然后有一些海洋生物，又有一些有趣的感觉。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">题外话，没有故事剧情是我的问题，主要我确实还不太会讲故事，等我去猛猛学。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里的提示词也非常简单，我就是先选中这张图，然后我们会看到这张图自动就在右下方对话框了。然后我提示词写的是：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 79, 235);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考这个风格不变，生成8张不同分镜和角度的女孩在海中生活的故事分镜，可以出现其他角色，保证人物一致性，可以换衣服。</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=48ea2915&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltmq9WoHLWHXBCGQ9jOgJ28lj0a1icQOCeT65s5zJ9bWXNQxvj55yuKpw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">系统提示强过我绞尽脑汁啊。Lovart 在我非常粗糙的指令下，还是输出了我满意的图片，个别细节有问题，直接选中修改就可以。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后就是 Hailuo 2.3 启动。这个没写其他提示词，只有对视频模型和 Lovart Agent 的考验👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.762962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b532e084&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltSHG2d6lrYNs1aUQyQoia72eGrQJZCPtCWlgc0P2SO06KrfWNrcubTdA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成结束的视频就是我前面放的《生活在海里的女孩》了。除了加速视频什么也没有做，Hailuo 2.3模型做动漫类的画风一致性与稳定性我愿称其目前最强。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">1080P 的画质也很感人，日常短片完全够用了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hailuo 2.3 其他的后期有空我继续发散，接下来给大家看看Lovart上新的另一个视频模型，LTX 2。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);line-height:1.6;border-style:dashed;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Lovart x LTX 2</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">LTX 2 可以4K视频输出，在AI生成视频这块直接杀出重围，速度还出奇快，我感觉比生成S*ra pro 模型能快10倍，视频时长现最长 在10秒据说后期会有20秒，并且音画同步，稳定性也不错，尤其做高帧率动态场景、广告等效果很好。口型匹配和旁白音乐也能行，可以说中文，偶尔有点别扭。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Lovart 直接用LTX 2，分辨率和速度都非常感人。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.512962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8a5a10c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDlt186hh1X7hMubRcwFU5y3QiaeyUknhDcsHzqf0ZTffrlfnqx8btOavxA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">高帧率动态场景真的很不错，先给大家呈上几个直出的视频看看效果。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面的视频的提示词都比较长，我会统一放在这个表格中，大家感兴趣的话可以去看看：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 79, 235);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://a80cyp5nki.feishu.cn/base/OlepbtQ1Ua66tos3NRlcRc8WnSf?from=from_copylink\" target=\"_blank\">https://a80cyp5nki.feishu.cn/base/OlepbtQ1Ua66tos3NRlcRc8WnSf?from=from_copylink</a></span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3D动画+甩镜头动态跟拍+仿手持晃动👇</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">赛博朋克+动态镜头+低角度跟拍+拉伸摇臂+航拍，（飞上天可能是我提示词的问题）崩了的细节我也保留在视频里了，瑕不掩瑜👇</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">奇幻风格+CG动画短片+FPV穿越机镜头，音效也好好👇</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">唱歌也可以（这组是文生视频）👇</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">真人的效果也可以，有个好玩的，就是模仿不同年代感的视频也行，比如模仿90年代美国脱口秀（这组是文生视频）👇</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">唱中文+微表情+中景，表情细节很好，中文水准差不多是这样哈哈哈👇</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">补充一个小技巧，如果要基于已生成视频修改细节，操作方法：选择视频后，上方会出现【Remix】，点击Remix就可以直接修改提示词和参考图、模型时长分辨率等细节了👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-radius: 8px;overflow: hidden;width: 98%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5879629629629629\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b37b2938&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHibrYDJehdiaeutVgLczVnVrvib6eUfzDltM3XX7PDL7ic1JLPnIia1njMOK0Le7II2HvF3yN65h8QGhdSsMFHFicjYw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;-webkit-box-reflect: below -1px -webkit-linear-gradient(top, transparent, transparent 93%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8));box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;padding: 2px;border-radius: 4px;margin-top: 0.8em;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(212, 141, 247) 0%, rgb(92, 79, 235) 80%);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:0px 15px;font-size:24px;border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);line-height:1.6;border-style:dashed;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小结</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 2;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Lovart 接入新模型速度是真的快，新出的图像分层功能也挺好的，对设计师友好，直接在画布里就能拆分编辑和重组。多个模型配合起来，能做的事情越来越多了。我后面还会继续深挖多个模型结合的更多玩法，到时候再来给大家分享。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">上次 Lovart 活动是年费会员限免了一个月S*ra 2 和 Veo 3.1，我休假去了没测哎嘿，这次是 Hailuo 2.3 模型和 LTX 2 视频模型，也是年费会员限免一个月，活动时间截止到 11 月 10 号。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">图片和视频生成方面消耗大的、需要切换多个模型的都可以考虑。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前还有朋友说希望看 Lovart 用法的视频，我也想着有空做一期视频简单讲讲一些基本操作和趣味玩法，做了的话到时候和大家说！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接再放一次👉&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 79, 235);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.lovart.ai/zh/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lovart.ai/zh/</a></span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">LTX 2 视频提示词表格再放一次👇</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 79, 235);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://a80cyp5nki.feishu.cn/wiki/Oxz8w8Jf2iTpixkGoJ6cukEwnfg\" target=\"_blank\">https://a80cyp5nki.feishu.cn/wiki/Oxz8w8Jf2iTpixkGoJ6cukEwnfg</a></span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果今天的内容大家觉得有趣或者有帮助，欢迎猛猛三连鼓励阿真，我还会继续努力探索更多工具、更新更多AI资讯、带来更多好内容的，非常感谢大家！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果觉得有更多有趣的玩法和看法，欢迎评论区留言，朋友们下期见！</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">下方有往期 Lovart 相关教程，都是很用心写哒，希望对朋友们有帮助～!👇</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "评测了 Lovart 平台新增的图像分层功能及集成的 Hailuo 2.3 和 LTX 2 视频模型，并分享了实际应用案例和使用技巧。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "评测了 Lovart 平台新增的图像分层功能及集成的 Hailuo 2.3 和 LTX 2 视频模型，并分享了实际应用案例和使用技巧。",
  "summary": "文章详细评测了 AI 创作平台 Lovart 的最新功能和模型集成。首先介绍了图像分层功能，展示了其在海报设计中独立编辑元素、调整光影的实用性，并提供了相关提示词技巧。接着，作者通过《少年打虎》和《生活在海里的女孩》两个短片制作案例，深入展示了 Hailuo 2.3 视频模型在动漫风格、动态稳定性和微表情处理上的优势，并分享了从剧本到视频生成的五步流程及分镜提示词。随后，文章重点介绍了 LTX 2 视频模型，强调其 4K 输出、高帧率动态场景、快速生成以及音画同步能力，并提供了多个不同风格的视频示例。最后总结了 Lovart 快速集成新模型的优势，并提醒读者关注限时会员免费试用活动。",
